Date of Birth: April 12, 1807<br/>
Birthplace: Burlington, New York, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: February 21, 1835<br/>
Death: May 13, 1857<br/>
<br/>
Born April 12, 1807, at Burlington, Otsego Co., New York, to Jared Pratt and Charity Dickinson.
Ordained apostle Feb. 21, 1835, under the hands of Joseph Smith, Oliver Cowdery, and David Whitmer, at Kirtland, Ohio, at age 27;
assassinated May 13, 1857, near Van Buren, Crawford Co., Arkansas, at age 50.